title: SUNDAY SERMON: Desire, Dissatisfaction, and Wrestling with Restlessness, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO258
itunes:title: SUNDAY SERMON: Desire, Dissatisfaction, and Wrestling with Restlessness, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO258
description: I’m finding it common to run into people who think they have found their purpose in life, but are still struggling with dissatisfaction on a daily basis. Restlessness is actually part of what it means to be a human being living in the real world. If you feel empty no matter how much you succeed, listen closely to today's episode. Vaughn, Tyler & myself talk about reasons for restlessness & dissatisfaction & what to do about it. If this is something you struggle with, just know this: YOU'RE NORMAL.
